{"tid":185030,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［年經］覺唔覺林夕真係好仆街","createTime":"2017-04-03T07:54:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-03T08:27:22.000Z","uid":88263,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"26242437940d839a6cc469ea9905d8bd88867e0d","tid":185030,"uid":88263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T07:54:57.000Z","msg":"離開你六十年 但願能認得出你的的子女<br />\n（愛一個人去到六十年後想認出佢嘅仔女，為想死前再講聲再見）<br />\n<br />\n在有生的瞬間能遇到你 竟花光所有運氣 到這日才發現 曾呼吸過空氣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n閉起雙眼我最掛念誰 眼睛張開身邊竟是誰<br />\n（你愛的人不愛你，愛你的人你不愛）<br />\n感激車站裡尚有月台 曾讓我們滿足到落淚<br />\n（車站中短暫相聚已經好滿足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n歌詞都可以殺人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"604d675ef3f0b7cb3b652483ce9d80e15b0109b0","tid":185030,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T07:58:27.000Z","msg":"推時光倒流二十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b398c50e2dadba0ffd3331b6f16eef7b2c289f4","tid":185030,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T07:59:49.000Z","msg":"或者二十年前就認識你 依家就唔會咁多遺憾<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0622dbea4f01977fb58677b8827d9fd048b8fe5","tid":185030,"uid":10325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T08:00:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbf25f58a43da89ebe577b98c21540124c697168","tid":185030,"uid":100542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T08:07:23.000Z","msg":"我覺得佢後期嗰啲愈聽愈出得多嘢，唔單止愛情，而係人生"},{"pid":"e72539786272f17e15a650f8b342202884bf735